      "content": "The feeling of being overwhelmed by endless treatment options and facing a seemingly inescapable pain is exhausting and frightening. When medical avenues feel like they are only managing, not solving, the pain, the despair can become immense. If thoughts of ending your life are becoming very strong, please contact a crisis resource immediately so you can speak with someone who understands the depth of this suffering. There are compassionate resources available right now to help hold space for this unbearable pain.",
